      <div>
        <h2 style="margin: 0 0 24px 0; color: #00bfff;">Our Story</h2>
        <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 16px;">
          Gordon Food Service (Galveston) was established to meet the unique provisioning needs of the Gulf Coast 
          energy sector. Located in the heart of Galveston's port district, we specialize in wholesale food, 
          water, and essential supplies for offshore rigs, vessels, and industrial operations.
        </p>
        <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 16px;">
          Our commitment to quality, reliability, and timely delivery has made us a trusted partner for major 
          energy companies operating in the Gulf of Mexico. We understand the critical nature of offshore 
          operations and the importance of maintaining crew welfare with quality provisions.
        </p>
        <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); line-height: 1.8; margin: 0;">
          From our strategically located warehouse in the 28th‚Äì36th Street Port/Harborside industrial zone, 
          we coordinate deliveries to offshore platforms, supply vessels, and onshore facilities within a 
          100-mile radius of Galveston.
        </p>
      </div>
